837
00:49:00,020 --> 00:49:01,520
What are you doing?

838
00:49:07,030 --> 00:49:09,030
Cleaning the closet.

839
00:49:10,530 --> 00:49:14,029
Can you... help me...

840
00:49:14,030 --> 00:49:16,030
