864
00:51:02,640 --> 00:51:06,140
To Edna...

865
00:51:09,150 --> 00:51:11,650
Well, I mailed
the gas payment instead.

866
00:51:12,150 --> 00:51:13,150
(chuckles)

867
00:51:16,660 --> 00:51:19,660
Have you ever heard
of anything so dumb?

868
00:51:20,160 --> 00:51:22,159
The gas company
is probably reading

869
00:51:22,160 --> 00:51:25,160
