872
00:51:32,170 --> 00:51:35,170
I know. I know.

873
00:51:35,180 --> 00:51:37,679
Hollis,

874
00:51:37,680 --> 00:51:39,679
Josie and I were just talking,

875
00:51:39,680 --> 00:51:44,680
