996
01:00:28,210 --> 01:00:31,209
Josie! Hey.

997
01:00:31,210 --> 01:00:32,210
(moans softly)

998
01:00:32,211 --> 01:00:34,209
Josie, we got to go!

999
01:00:34,210 --> 01:00:37,219
