1050
01:04:07,436 --> 01:04:08,929
What if it starts to rain?

1051
01:04:08,930 --> 01:04:10,929
You bring umbrellas, too?

1052
01:04:10,930 --> 01:04:12,430
How about a pasta maker

1053
01:04:12,930 --> 01:04:13,430
